  - m_Id: 702346153984
    m_Localized: Tost Makinesi
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 703260512256
    m_Localized: "<ON_GAME_START>, rastgele ceplere 2 <TOAST> f\u0131rlat."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 704338448384
    m_Localized: "Kara Delik \xC7ekirde\u011Fi"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 705189892096
    m_Localized: "<ON_POCKET>, yak\u0131ndaki toplar\u0131 \xE7eker."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 706242662400
    m_Localized: Acil Durum Kiti
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 707127660544
    m_Localized: If you can't reach the <TARGET_SCORE> with your last <SHOT>, give
      you another <SHOT>, once. Given <SHOT> also add a +2 <MULT>. Disable after
      trigger.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 708184625152
    m_Localized: Numbers II
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 709069623296
    m_Localized: "<ON_GAME_START>, 10 <POINT> de\u011Ferli 1x <NUMBERS_BALL> <SPAWN>.\n<NUMBERS_1>
      \u015Fartt\u0131r."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 710118199296
    m_Localized: "Alt\u0131n Kupa"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 710973837312
    m_Localized: "<ON_BOUNCE>, +1<COIN> verir ama art\u0131k <BOUNCE_POINT> olmaz.\n<ON_TURN_END>,
      sahip oldu\u011Fun her <COIN> i\xE7in +1 <MULT>."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 712039190528
    m_Localized: Numbers III
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 712886439936
    m_Localized: "<ON_GAME_START>, 100 <POINT> de\u011Ferli 1x <NUMBERS_BALL> <SPAWN>.\n<NUMBERS_10>
      \u015Fartt\u0131r."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 713943404544
    m_Localized: "Delge\xE7"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 714828402688
    m_Localized: <ON_GAME_END>+1<COIN>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 715914727424
    m_Localized: "Tan\u0131mlay\u0131c\u0131"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 716753588224
    m_Localized: <ON_TURN_END> +1 <COIN>
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 717797969920
    m_Localized: Kitaplar
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 718636830720
    m_Localized: "\u0130kinci ni\u015Fan \xE7izgisini etkinle\u015Ftirir"
